        """

            cur_language, ["de", "es", "fr", "pl", "ro", "ru", "zh"])
        Common().check_language_in_list_and_skip_if_present(cur_country, ["gb"])
    
        page_conditions = Conditions(d, "")
        main_page_link = page_conditions.preconditions(
